# Project
# Ignore the .freelance/ directory's contents by default, but keep
# committed workflows listed explicitly below so the MCP server can
# auto-load them and others can reference them. Uses the "ignore
# contents then un-ignore specifics" pattern (.freelance/ as a directory
# pattern would swallow un-ignores).
.freelance/*
!.freelance/memory-architecture-port.workflow.yaml
.claude/settings.local.json
docs/
